    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, preheat the grill to high</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong>&nbsp;and finely dice the carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> and finely dice the onion<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> and finely chop (or grate) the garlic</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cut</strong> the lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> in half&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
