      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, slice the chicken into strips</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the yoghurt, garlic, curry powder and chicken strips to a mixing bowl with the juice of half a&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">(whole)</span> lemon and season generously with salt and pepper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reserve</strong> the remaining lemon for later</p>",
